## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="6fa68-1085"><xref:System.Collections.Generic?displayProperty=nameWithType> 命名空間中集合的預設實作未同步處理。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6fa68-1085">Default implementations of collections in the <xref:System.Collections.Generic?displayProperty=nameWithType> namespace are not synchronized.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="6fa68-1086">透過集合進行列舉在本質上並非安全執行緒程序。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6fa68-1086">Enumerating through a collection is intrinsically not a thread-safe procedure.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="6fa68-1087">若要確保列舉期間的執行緒安全性，您可以在整個列舉期間鎖定集合。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6fa68-1087">To guarantee thread safety during enumeration, you can lock the collection during the entire enumeration.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="6fa68-1088">若要讓多重執行緒能夠存取集合以便進行讀取和寫入，您必須實作自己的同步處理。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6fa68-1088">To allow the collection to be accessed by multiple threads for reading and writing, you must implement your own synchronization.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="6fa68-1089"><xref:System.Collections.ICollection.SyncRoot%2A> 傳回的物件，可用來同步存取<xref:System.Collections.ICollection>。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6fa68-1089"><xref:System.Collections.ICollection.SyncRoot%2A> returns an object that can be used to synchronize access to the <xref:System.Collections.ICollection>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="6fa68-1090">同步處理是所有執行緒存取集合之前都鎖定這個物件時，才有效。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6fa68-1090">Synchronization is effective only if all threads lock this object before accessing the collection.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="6fa68-1091">下列程式碼示範如何使用<xref:System.Collections.ICollection.SyncRoot%2A>C#、 c + + 和 Visual Basic 的屬性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6fa68-1091">The following code shows the use of the <xref:System.Collections.ICollection.SyncRoot%2A> property for C#, C++, and Visual Basic.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
ICollection ic = ...;  
lock (ic.SyncRoot)   
{  
    // Access the collection.  
}  
```  
  
```vb  
Dim ic As ICollection = ...  
SyncLock ic.SyncRoot  
    ' Access the collection.  
End SyncLock  
```  
  
```cpp#  
ICollection^ ic = ...;  
try   
{  
    Monitor::Enter(ic->SyncRoot);  
    // Access the collection.  
}  
finally   
{  
    Monitor::Exit(ic->SyncRoot);  
}  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="6fa68-1092">擷取這個屬性的值是一種 O(1) 運算。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6fa68-1092">Retrieving the value of this property is an O(1) operation.</span></span>
